
    USAGE

        door [config] [options]

    CONFIG

       Any JSON file.

       Example:

        {
          "foo.com": "localhost:3001",
          "bar.net": "localhost:3002",
          "static.net": "/home/azer/sites/bar.net"
        }


    OPTIONS

        -p      --port        Target port.
        -d      --daemon      Run as daemon on the background.
        -s      --stop        Stop the running daemon.
        -v      --version     Show version and exit.
        -h      --help        Show this help and exist.

    DEBUG

      DEBUG=door:* door config.json
